[23.31, "o", "+- plan preview . dry run, no execution -------------------------------------------------------+\r\n|                                                                                              |\r\n|  load CSVs into Snowflake RAW, build CORE silver and MART gold, then drop                    |\r\n|  MART.DAILY_REVENUE                                                                          |\r\n|                                                                                              |\r\n|  step                                       decision      rollback                           |\r\n|  load CSVs into Snowflake RAW, build CORE…  confirm - n…  zero_copy_clone (verified at e…    |\r\n|  drop MART.DAILY_REVENUE  (after s1)        dry_run+app…  no native undo - would be refu…    |\r\n|                                                                                              |\r\n|  2 step(s)  .  2 need(s) approval  .  nothing was executed                                   |\r\n|                                                                                              |\r\n|  tiers  safe  .  write  .  risky  .  irreversible                                            |\r\n|                                                                                              |\r\n+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\r\n"]
